queries.sql:
select *, tu.status, tp.position,tu.added_on, tu.updated_on
        from tbl_users as tu, tbl_firm as tf, tbl_position as tp
        where tu.firm = tf.firmID
        and tu.position = tp.posID
        and tu.userID != 1
